race.description: Jack Primmer Electronics F&M Maiden Handicap
race.comment: FRANKELY SUBLIME (1) made steady inroads to finish runner-up when resuming over 1250m at Newcastle last start. Gets a few gear changes today which is interesting. Coming back 50m isn't ideal but she looks to be in good order and can improve off that first-up effort. ALABAMA HUSSY (14) missed the kick then made up a little late ground without threatening first-up over this distance at Nowra. In the money here at this distance when second-up last prep. Can make plenty of progress off that latest effort. ME ME (3) is back after a six-month break. Raced just twice last prep and attacked the line with purpose on each occasion to get up for second in 1200m maidens. Expecting another forward showing. OUR HUNTRESS (5) on debut is the interesting runner. Trials have been okay but the weight of early money suggests she is pretty smart. GONG GIRL (11) worked through the line strongly on debut at Goulburn and will appreciate the extra 100m today.
